<pb ed="T" id="T20.1037.0019c" n="0019c"/>
<lb n="0019c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0019c02"/>
<lb n="0019c03"/><head type="no">No. 1037 [No. 1038]</head>
<lb n="0019c04"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0019007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十六，【乙】承保三年寫仁和寺藏本</note>觀自在菩薩說普賢陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0019c05"/>
<lb n="0019c06"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0019008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（開府…門）四十一字＝（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十七字【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】，（唐三藏沙門大廣智）八字【明】</note><note n="0019008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（開府…門）四十一字＝（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智）十七字【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】，＝（唐三藏沙門大廣智）八字【明】</note><app n="0019008" word-count="41"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅國
<lb n="0019c07"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0019c08"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">唐三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0019c09"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0019c10"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時薄伽梵住王舍城靈鷲山。與
<lb n="0019c11"/>大苾芻眾及大菩薩<note n="0019009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔摩訶薩〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019009"><lem>摩訶薩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>九十九俱胝眾
<lb n="0019c12"/>俱。</p>
<lb n="0019c13"/><p>爾時聖觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。在彼眾會從座
<lb n="0019c14"/>而起。白佛言世尊我欲顯說普賢陀羅尼。世
<lb n="0019c15"/>尊此陀羅尼。我於月上光如來所<note n="0019010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝授【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019010"><lem>受</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">授</rdg></app>得。若
<lb n="0019c16"/>菩薩乘者。纔聞此陀羅尼。即得不退轉。速疾
<lb n="0019c17"/>承事一切如來應供正遍知者。能銷滅一切
<lb n="0019c18"/>業障獲得安樂富饒。身得清淨語業清淨意
<lb n="0019c19"/>得清淨。通達一<note n="0019011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">切＋（大智）【三】，（大切）【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0019011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切＋（大智）【宋】【元】【明】，（大切）【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019011"><lem>切</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">切大智</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">切大切</rdg></app>大<note n="0019012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔祕〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019012"><lem>祕</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>密海。能滿一切大
<lb n="0019c20"/>願海。即見一切如來。我由<note n="0019013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔聞〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019013"><lem>聞</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>此陀羅尼。便
<lb n="0019c21"/>證無生法忍。獲得首楞嚴三摩地。證得寶印
<lb n="0019c22"/>三摩地<note n="0019014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔焰炬…地〕十字－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019014" word-count="10"><lem>焰炬三摩地海印三摩地</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>普遍虛空
<lb n="0019c23"/>三摩地。證得如是等琲e沙數三摩地門。復
<lb n="0019c24"/>證得<note n="0019015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">開＝聞【宋】</note><app n="0019015"><lem>開</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">聞</rdg></app>無盡篋等八萬四千陀羅尼門。由此
<lb n="0019c25"/>證得具慧具行。得如是智慧。成就所聞<note n="0019016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0019016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0019016"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0019c26"/>法。於諸佛所聞法無<note n="0019017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">間＝聞【宋】</note><app n="0019017"><lem>間</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">聞</rdg></app>承事供養。<note n="0019018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】</note><note n="0019018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0019018"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願世
<lb n="0019c27"/>尊許我為四部眾說。佛言聽汝宣說。</p>
<lb n="0019c28"/><p>爾時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。入金剛曼<note n="0019019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">荼＝茶【宋】【元】【甲】＊</note><app n="0019019"><lem>荼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">茶</rdg></app>羅三
<lb n="0019c29"/>摩地。即說陀羅尼曰。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1037.0020a" n="0020a"/>
<lb n="0020a01"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0020001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梵字真言附載於卷末 cf. P. 21a</note>曩莫囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>野耶<note place="inline">一</note>曩莫阿<note place="inline">引</note>哩
<lb n="0020a02"/>耶<note place="inline">二<note n="0020002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">合＋（二）【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合＋（二）【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020002"><lem>合</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">合二</rdg></app></note>&CB00085;盧枳帝濕&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>囉<note n="0020003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【乙】＊</note><app n="0020003"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0020004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＋（三）夾註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶＋（三）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020004"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">耶<note place="inline">三</note></rdg></app>&CB00155;地薩
<lb n="0020a03"/>怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note><note n="0020005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＋（四）夾註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野＋（四）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020005"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">野<note place="inline">四</note></rdg></app>摩訶薩怛&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>野<note place="inline"><note n="0020006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝五【三】【甲】</note><note n="0020006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝五【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0020006"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">五</rdg></app></note>摩訶<note place="inline">引</note>迦
<lb n="0020a04"/><app type="＊" source="0020003"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app>嚕抳迦<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0020007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＋（六）夾註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野＋（六）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020007"><lem>野</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">野<note place="inline">六</note></rdg></app>怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合<note n="0020008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【三】，引＝反【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔引〕－【宋】【元】【明】，引＝反【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020008"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">反</rdg></app></note><note n="0020009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">他＋（七）夾註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">他＋（七）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020009"><lem>他</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">他<note place="inline">七</note></rdg></app>佉<note place="inline"><note n="0020010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＋（聲）【明】＊</note><app n="0020010"><lem>上</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">上聲</rdg></app></note>&CB00344;吠
<lb n="0020a05"/>佉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0020010"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note>&CB00344;吠佉<note place="inline"><app type="＊" source="0020010"><lem>上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">上聲</rdg></app></note><note n="0020011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＝&CB00344;【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020011"><lem>我</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&CB00344;</rdg></app><note n="0020012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吠＋（八）夾註【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0020012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吠＋（八）夾註【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020012"><lem>吠</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吠<note place="inline">八</note></rdg></app>斫屈芻<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0020013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">佉＋（九）夾註【三】</note><note n="0020013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佉＋（九）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0020013"><lem>佉</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">佉<note place="inline">九</note></rdg></app><note n="0020014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吠＋（九）夾註【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0020014"><lem>吠</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">吠<note place="inline">九</note></rdg></app>&CB02122;
